keras_model_sequential() %>% layer_dense(units = FLAGS$nodes_layer1, 
    activation = "relu", input_shape = ncol(x)) %>% layer_batch_normalization() %>% 
    layer_dropout(rate = FLAGS$dropout_layer1) %>% layer_dense(units = FLAGS$nodes_layer2, 
    activation = "relu") %>% layer_batch_normalization() %>% 
    layer_dropout(rate = FLAGS$dropout_layer2) %>% layer_dense(units = FLAGS$nodes_layer3, 
    activation = "relu") %>% layer_batch_normalization() %>% 
    layer_dropout(rate = FLAGS$dropout_layer3) %>% layer_dense(units = 2, 
    activation = "sigmoid") %>% compile(loss = "categorical_crossentropy", 
    optimizer = optimizer_rmsprop(), metrics = "roc") %>% fit(x = x, 
    y = y, epochs = 50, batch_size = 256, validation_split = 0.2, 
    callbacks = list(callback_early_stopping(patience = 20), 
        callback_reduce_lr_on_plateau()), verbose = 2)
